      <h3>What is it?</h3>
        <p>Three hours of remote or on-site pairing with an experienced thoughtbot developer. We'll work on a project of your choosing and observe your proficiency with your editor, shell, source control, Ruby, and Rails. During the pairing we'll offer constructive feedback for improving your workflow and code. After the session, we'll spend another hour writing up some exercises and reading recommendations to shore up your weakest areas. Additionally, you can (and should!) have a second colleague join the session for free, so you can help reinforce the new habits in each other.</p>

