      <p>Rubyists of any level that are strongly motivated to improve themselves. This program is particularly suited for those without access to a more-experienced mentor.</p>

      <h3>What skills will I improve?</h3>
      <p>We can be particularly helpful in improving the following areas: writing maintainable Ruby, understanding and implementing OO design principles, crafting idiomatic Rails code, awareness of useful gems, improving your git workflow, and increasing vim proficiency (if you use it).</p>

