      <p>If you're local to Boston or can get here, we'd love to have you join us at our beautiful offices. You can bring your own laptop or we'll provide one for you, along with a giant monitor and external keyboard and mouse. If you're remote, we'll set up a screen-sharing session and video chat. Finally, we'll record the entire session and provide you a free copy.</p>

      <h3>When will this happen?</h3>
      <p>We'll work with you to schedule a convenient time. We're pretty flexible.</p>
